---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact Us">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-6">Contact Us</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-surface max-w-none text-surface-600 space-y-4">
      <p>We value your feedback and inquiries. Whether you have a question about a <a href="/compare" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">product comparison</a>, want to report a pricing error, or are interested in partnering with us, we would love to hear from you. Browse our <a href="/hubs" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">SSD buying guides</a> or <a href="/about" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">learn more about us</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>Email us directly at: <a href="mailto:support@externalssds.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">support@externalssds.com</a></p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Business Address</h2>
      <p>Competitive LLC<br />
      <span class="text-surface-400 italic">(Address available upon request)</span></p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Response Time</h2>
      <p>We aim to respond to all inquiries within 1-2 business days.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
